      <title>休斯顿最古老的炼油厂正在关闭。这不会是最后一个。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-15/houston-s-oldest-refinery-is-shutting-it-won-t-be-the-last</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在休斯顿船舶频道的河岸上了一个多世纪的燃料之后，该市最古老的炼油厂正准备关闭，并有可能使数百人失业。它的竞争对手欢迎其灭亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-15/houston-s-oldest-refinery-is-shutting-it-won-t-be-the-last</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Feb 2025 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
